oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Williams. Gen. Alpheus S. Williams.
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: unknown
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: General Alpheus Starkey Williams. Member of the Thirteenth (13th) Tennessee Union Cavalry or the Thirteenth Regiment, Tennessee Volunteer Cavalry, U.S.A. This unit was involved with the Bridge Burnings in East Tennessee during the Civil War.
